comment_data.body:
@blueyed Someone left a bug report for Firefox regarding CRLF markers, but honestly I'm not sure it's upstream enough. I think GTK3 should use LF marker for line breaks on Linux because QT5 applications don't have this problem.

Interesting issue to be honest. It's either a design choice by GTK or a bug.

https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1572104
